{"tid":2238904,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"切燒豬 女警司叫40下屬除罩  賀歸隊兼慶生「開心啲」議員斥律己以寬","createTime":"2020-10-11T13:25:53.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-11T14:12:02.000Z","uid":25558,"like":7,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"2c801cc9aa2739910c20891053b34d5ae2e25727","tid":2238904,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-11T13:25:53.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20201011/ONHFJXTM3VEGNJMCQA37MDECC4/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20201011%2FONHFJXTM3VEGNJMCQA37MDECC4%2F&d=bDSN5K49m9pAVz54ArwUlVKEWDR5zjN73Co06CeqttY%3D&h=28cabcd1\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20201011%2FONHFJXTM3VEGNJMCQA37MDECC4%2F&h=5572470b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20201011/ONHFJXTM3VEGNJMCQA37MDECC4/</a><br />\n<br />\n節錄<br />\n<br />\n切燒豬 女警司叫40下屬除罩 <br />\n賀歸隊兼慶生「開心啲」議員斥律己以寬<br />\n<br />\n【明知故犯】<br />\n<br />\n相關新聞：帝苑女工消毒無着保護衣<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】武漢肺炎疫情反覆，近日確診個案曾回復雙位數，更有五星級酒店要休業及爆發酒吧群組，但身為執行限聚令的警隊卻疑漠視播毒風險。前日在葵涌警署就有41名警員疑為慶祝防暴隊員回歸分區警署，除罩零距離大合照，包括葵涌分區警署女指揮官潘瑞屏警司。立法會議員兼醫生郭家麒批評做法不理想，指事件反映警隊防疫意識低，但對市民執行限聚令卻極嚴厲，予人律己以寬、待人以嚴的壞印象。<br />\n<br />\n近月隨着示威抗爭事件減少，警方逐步解散防暴隊，不少防暴隊隊員回歸原來工作崗位。。。。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n相關新聞：臨檢中心開放 料日驗千樣本<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/dOCSlxyA-OoIwTy2EDxxZSCyNVA=/1228x733/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/VXFHOGQVANHDHAGB36LGEAQEB4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FdOCSlxyA-OoIwTy2EDxxZSCyNVA%3D%2F1228x733%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FVXFHOGQVANHDHAGB36LGEAQEB4.jpg&h=e86b0a7d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■有讀者向本報提供潘瑞屏警司及40名下屬的除罩合照，相中更加上「播毒」、「害下屬」等字句。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/FX6Sv6fBbcuFCIAYqnM8maVBLgE=/677x516/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/FOEN2XMQCZGXVGLXHL3THRCCL4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FFX6Sv6fBbcuFCIAYqnM8maVBLgE%3D%2F677x516%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FFOEN2XMQCZGXVGLXHL3THRCCL4.jpg&h=6147a35b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■潘瑞屏2015年獲盧偉聰擢升為警司。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n警拒交代會否懲處<br />\n<br />\n知情人士指，聚會開始時在場40多名警員都有戴上口罩，但其後女警司疑為讓大家「開心啲」，即指令全場41人除下口罩近距離大合照。。。。。。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n警方發言人回應時承認，葵青警區人員前日早上於葵涌警署舉行簡單歡迎儀式，曾短暫脫下口罩拍照留念。發言人強調一直密切留意有關2019冠狀病毒疫情發展，並不時提醒同事減少社交接觸，避免群組聚集，留意自身健康狀況，如有任何不適，需立即呈報並求醫；惟未有交代會否有進一步跟進或懲處行動。<br />\n<br />\n過去亦發生警員除口罩合照事件，。。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n今次涉事的女警司潘瑞屏加入警隊22年，2015年獲晉升為警司，翌年曾以人事部人力資源研究組警司身份，代表警隊獲明愛青少年及社區服務處頒發「傑出成長嚮導同盟大獎」，表揚為非華語學生提供投考警隊資訊，助他們拓闊視野規劃未來，同年獲警務處頒發香港警察長期服務獎章。<br />\n<br />\n去年反修例活動風波，。。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n立法會議員兼醫生郭家麒指，根據《預防及控制疾病（佩戴口罩）規例》（第599I章）只規定室內公眾場所必須佩戴口罩，有關警務人員在警署內除罩並不違法，但警隊出外執行限聚令時態度嚴苛，被批向巿民濫發告票，但自己人群聚的防疫意識卻極低，「尤其係切完燒豬一齊食埋，咁樣感染風險好高，公務員食堂都唔容許咁多人一齊，佢哋咁做係做咗壞榜樣，畀人感覺好唔專業。」<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/CGc5daICB3pDXFZbmiRgV2I_euE=/1330x886/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/DOFAPNSIBNHMRMGF6WPV6SY4SI.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FCGc5daICB3pDXFZbmiRgV2I_euE%3D%2F1330x886%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FDOFAPNSIBNHMRMGF6WPV6SY4SI.jpg&h=68476227&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■警方多次寬己嚴人，今年7月有400名防暴警在粉嶺基地操場合照，被指漠視限聚令。"},{"pid":"773f3c226afd3b20431d3179621a320ab6701197","tid":2238904,"uid":285166,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-11T13:27:57.000Z","msg":"人地揸槍 有乜唔做得"},{"pid":"27f7feddf2a042f227da68396048c0aa4d98e6e6","tid":2238904,"uid":335434,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-11T13:32:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://i.pinimg.com/originals/25/7d/10/257d105b797d7521641c29a204d8bc21.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.pinimg.com%2Foriginals%2F25%2F7d%2F10%2F257d105b797d7521641c29a204d8bc21.jpg&h=ed6ae34d&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"334bc17b8b736016d7811e361e51fd8e55a224d2","tid":2238904,"uid":160102,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-11T13:34:33.000Z","msg":"成班垃圾"},{"pid":"3d72e9e66de759fb2259eedb91a20ad6141227b7","tid":2238904,"uid":299514,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-11T13:54:09.000Z","msg":"自爆點相<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9c09263072a52e92362f6fb5541eff10b7342ae2","tid":2238904,"uid":6058,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-11T13:55:12.000Z","msg":"我打咗上去要求報警喇<br />\n但佢話<span class=\"red\"><span class=\"xx-large\">警署係私人地方</span></span><br />\n私人地方係限聚令豁免<br />\n不過唔知點解法例話工作場所都受限聚令規範<br />\n可能警署唔係工作地方啦<br />\n麻煩議員跟一跟"},{"pid":"e1a30f9414a921913b0def6df576a7ea3dca1b92","tid":2238904,"uid":21545,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-11T14:08:49.000Z","msg":"41p<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7d25d230130edfba12760f531fe5c7abc0e72ebb","tid":2238904,"uid":122083,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"e1a30f9414a921913b0def6df576a7ea3dca1b92","tid":2238904,"uid":21545,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-11T14:08:49.000Z","msg":"41p<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-11T14:12:02.000Z","msg":"你計漏左隻燒豬<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}